### @name loginSuccessUser
### ✅ Login com credenciais válidas (usuário comum)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### @name loginSuccessAdmin
