  "email": "email-invalido",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### ❌ Senha muito curta (erro de validação)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "password": "123"
}

### ❌ Usuário inexistente (erro de negócio)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "naoexiste@email.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### ❌ Senha incorreta (erro de negócio)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "password": "senhaErrada"
}

### ❌ Campos extras (forbidNonWhitelisted)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "password": "senha123",
  "campoExtra": "nao-permitido"
}

### ⚠️ Teste de Rate Limit (brute force)
### Execute essa request 6x em menos de 1 minuto.
### Esperado: as primeiras tentativas falham com 401 e a 6a com 429.
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "password": "senhaErrada"
}
